getting off the pill and trying to conceive read this it may help ok so i got off the pill in may and my husband and i are trying to concieve i am a healthy year old when i got off the pill i don't think i had ovulated the past months but the past days i had egg white cervical mucus the day i expected my period i guess that my system is getting back to normal so for you guys that are trying after birth control i now believe that the sayings are right that your body does need some time to get back to normal good luck to everyone and baby dust all around we are now in the week wait so wish us luck i felt it was necessary to share my experiences with everyone who is trying to concieve thank you for sharing sounds like your body is getting back to normal good luck and lots of baby dust Menstrual cycle Fertility awareness Pregnancy Emergency contraception Oral contraceptive Birth control Childbirth Ovulation Infertility Urinary incontinence Endometriosis Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Psoriasis EastEnders Miscarriage Puberty Social rule Breech birth Breastfeeding Mucus Alanis Morissette The Beatles discography In vitro fertilisation Hormone replacement therapy (trans) Apollo 8 Multiple birth Egg (food) Guinea pig Progesterone Niddah Cervix Neighbours Sharon Tate Time Out of Mind Hall & Oates Sonic the Hedgehog 2 Luck Abortion debate Infantilism Time Sexual abstinence Theory of conduct Stomach cancer Simone Weil Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Tocopherol Platypus Cystic fibrosis Cool (song) Elephant Sant Thakar Singh AIDS Guess Who's Coming to Criticize Dinner? Pitaten AFI 100 Years series Rod Stewart Androgen insensitivity syndrome Game show Singlish The Care Bears Adventure in Wonderland Jon Secada Pet Sounds The Chemical Brothers The Curse of Fenric Reservoir Dogs Ovary Intact dilation and extraction The Contender (television series) Human cloning Ovarian cyst Ovum Extrasolar planet Sexual reproduction USS Yorktown (CV-10) Slow Train Coming Grumpy's Three Wishes Maya calendar Beag